Package io.debezium.connector.mysql.antlr.listener

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlterTableParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL ALTER TABLE statements.
    AlterViewParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL ALTER VIEW statements.
    ColumnDefinitionParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing column definition part of MySQL statements.
    CreateAndAlterDatabaseParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL CREATE DATABASE and ALTER DATABASE statements, to get default character sets for database.
    CreateTableParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL CREATE TABLE statements.
    CreateUniqueIndexParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL CREATE UNIQUE INDEX statements, that will be used as a primary key if it's not already defined for the table.
    CreateViewParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL CREATE VIEW statements.
    DropDatabaseParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL DROP DATABASE statements.
    DropTableParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL DROP TABLE statements.
    DropViewParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL DROP VIEW statements.
    MySqlAntlrDdlParserListener
    Parser listener for MySQL column definition queries.
    RenameTableParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL RENAME TABLE statements.
    SetStatementParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL SET statements, for defining a system variables.
    TruncateTableParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL TRUNCATE TABLE statements.
    UseStatementParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL USE statements that changes current database/schema on which all changes are applied.
    ViewSelectedColumnsParserListener
    Parser listeners that is parsing MySQL SELECT statements used for definition of VIEW.
